    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到虚拟空间“Void Path”。这是一个以日本住宅区为背景的虚拟空间，除了你之外没有其他人。你的目标是到达这个空间的出口。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/343c98159cec0330558794ada8ebf47c.poster.avif?t=1730257294\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/343c98159cec0330558794ada8ebf47c.webm?t=1730257294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/343c98159cec0330558794ada8ebf47c.mp4?t=1730257294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个空间里，你只有小孩那么大，身高只有140厘米，但不用担心。不会有怪异的怪物追你或突然出现在你面前攻击你。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/4313be9a1d0e63811a30af85f75a0e2a.poster.avif?t=1730257294\" width=612 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/4313be9a1d0e63811a30af85f75a0e2a.webm?t=1730257294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/4313be9a1d0e63811a30af85f75a0e2a.mp4?t=1730257294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可能会有一点恐怖，但没什么大不了的。你会很容易到达出口。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/46135f002fe92c1f89ae905c3ba3cf02.poster.avif?t=1730257294\" width=624 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/46135f002fe92c1f89ae905c3ba3cf02.webm?t=1730257294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039060/extras/46135f002fe92c1f89ae905c3ba3cf02.mp4?t=1730257294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虚拟空间是一个不稳定的地方。切勿偏离常规路线，否则系统可能会崩溃。与可疑物体互动是不可能的。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就这些。享受你的“Void Path”吧！</p>",
